<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.181492>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11 – 16. Wagnerinus frugivorus Yoshitake. 11. Front tibia, male. 12. Mid tibia, male. 13. Hind tibia, male. 14. Venter, male. 15. Ventrites III – V, male. 16. Pygidium, male. Scale: 0.20 mm for 11 – 13; 0.50 mm for 14, 15; 0.25 mm for 16." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/181492/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.181490>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2, 3. Wagnerinus frugivorus Yoshitake. 2. Dorsal habitus. 3. Lateral habitus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/181490/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.181494>
    dc:description "FIGURES 24 – 28. Wagnerinus frugivorus Yoshitake. 24. Host plant, Weigela middendorffiana. 25. Habitat in Aizankei, Kamikawa, Hokkaido. 26. Adult on a leaf of W. middendorffiana. 27. Third-instar larva in a seed capsule of W. middendorffiana. 28. Pupa in the soil." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/181494/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.181491>
    dc:description "FIGURES 4 – 10. Wagnerinus frugivorus Yoshitake. 4. Dorsal view of head, male. 5. Lateral view of head, male. 6. Antennal space. 7. Antennal funicle. 8. Dorsal view of prothorax. 9. Lateral view of prothorax. 10. Elytron. Scale: 0.50 mm for 4, 5, 8, 9; 0.20 mm for 6, 7; 1.00 mm for 10." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/181491/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.181493>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17 – 23. Wagnerinus frugivorus Yoshitake. 17 – 20. Male genitalia. 17. Dorsal view of aedeagus. 18. Lateral view of aedeagus. 19. Sternite IX. 20. Tegmen. 21 – 23. Female genitalia. 21. Sternite VIII. 22. Ovipositor. 23. Spermatheca. Scale: 0.20 mm for 17 – 20; 0.10 mm for 21 – 23." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/181493/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

